## ‚ú® Interactive Effects

### GlowingEffect Component
Use the `<GlowingEffect />` component for interactive hover glow:

```tsx
<div className="relative">
  <GlowingEffect 
    proximity={64}    // Glow activation distance
    spread={30}       // Glow size
    blur={0}          // Blur amount
    variant="default" // or "white"
    glow={true}       // Enable glow effect
  />
  {/* Your content */}
</div>
```

**When to use**:
- Cards that should respond to mouse proximity
- Interactive sections
- Important CTAs
- Hero sections

### Reveal on Scroll Animation
```css
.reveal-on-scroll {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(24px);
  transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  transition-delay: var(--reveal-delay, 0ms);
}

.reveal-on-scroll.is-visible {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateY(0);
}
```

**Usage**: Add `.reveal-on-scroll` class and use `useRevealOnScroll()` hook.

### Hero Glow
Position large ambient glow in hero sections:
```css
.hero-glow {
  position: absolute;
  right: -220px;
  top: -80px;
  width: 480px;
  height: 480px;
  background: radial-gradient(
    circle, 
    rgba(255, 137, 70, 0.25), 
    rgba(4, 4, 5, 0)
  );
  filter: blur(40px);
  z-index: -2;
}
```

