### Standard Durations
- **Fast**: 150-200ms (micro-interactions)
- **Medium**: 300ms (hover effects, state changes)
- **Slow**: 600ms (reveal animations, page transitions)

### Easing
- **ease**: Default for most animations
- **ease-out**: Exits and reveals
- **ease-in-out**: Smooth two-way transitions

