## ‚ôø Accessibility Rules

### MUST DO
1. ‚úÖ All buttons must have `type="button"` attribute
2. ‚úÖ All SVG icons need `aria-label` and `role="img"`
3. ‚úÖ Interactive elements need keyboard handlers (`onKeyDown`)
4. ‚úÖ Focus states visible for keyboard navigation
5. ‚úÖ Color contrast ratio > 4.5:1 for text
6. ‚úÖ Alt text for all images
7. ‚úÖ Semantic HTML (headings hierarchy, landmarks)

### Interactive Elements
```tsx
{/* Clickable div - needs keyboard support */}
<div
  onClick={handleClick}
  onKeyDown={(e) => {
    if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') {
      e.preventDefault();
      handleClick();
    }
  }}
  role="button"
  tabIndex={0}
>
  {/* Content */}
</div>
```

