## üö´ DON'Ts - Common Mistakes to Avoid

### Colors
- ‚ùå Don't use pure white (#fff) - use --foreground (#f4f4f6)
- ‚ùå Don't use pure black (#000) - use --background (#040405)
- ‚ùå Don't use colors outside the palette
- ‚ùå Don't use solid borders - always use rgba with transparency

### Effects
- ‚ùå Don't use excessive glow (keep opacity < 0.5)
- ‚ùå Don't skip the backdrop-filter on glass cards
- ‚ùå Don't use animations longer than 600ms
- ‚ùå Don't animate expensive properties (use transform/opacity)

### Typography
- ‚ùå Don't use font sizes below 0.75rem (12px)
- ‚ùå Don't use more than 2 font families
- ‚ùå Don't use font-weight below 400
- ‚ùå Don't skip letter-spacing on uppercase text

### Layout
- ‚ùå Don't exceed max-width of 1160px for content
- ‚ùå Don't use arbitrary padding values (stick to spacing scale)
- ‚ùå Don't forget mobile responsiveness
- ‚ùå Don't use fixed widths (use max-width instead)

